{"title":"在琴房里","authors":["蒯天"],"dates":[{"year":1989,"month":5,"day":13}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"在琴房里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蒯天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你，一动也不动"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"背朝着门"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朝着门外的垂柳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朝着枝条拂皱的春池"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朝着绿水上滑来滑去的燕子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的手指伏在琴弦上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像树根"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生长着寂寞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"邀你微笑的风"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在音箱里四处碰壁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"然后，呜咽着走开了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你雕塑般伏在琴架上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是怕遗落心中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那支吟唱了万遍的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"暗淡的记忆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"难以烛亮你此时的情绪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哦！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多想扳过你的肩"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唤你走出你的悲哀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拨响垂柳的竖琴"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让那憧憬的乐曲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如轻盈的飞燕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"剪出一个多情的季节"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}